<chapter>
    <title>Service Level Management</title>
    <para>
        The OTRS stats framework has been completely revised for version
        2.1 and nearly every type of ticket report can be created in the web
        interface. Generation and view of stats and charts can be activated
        for users, groups and/or roles. It is possible to import or export
        existing or new stats and further use can be made of stats modules
        from previous OTRS versions.
        With the installation of the ITSMServiceLevelManagement package,
        additional ITSM relevant statistics are available.
    </para>
